	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For anyone who?s ever needed to sell someone on the merits of visual communication ? or wondered about the value of using it themselves ? we?ve created an all-in-one resource to answer your questions with facts: a new microsite!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">?</span><a href="https://visualcommunication.agency/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Visual Communication: The Future of Content Marketing</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">? was created to share the data and research we?ve collected over the years showing the importance and effectiveness of well-executed visual communication. Much like our </span><a href="http://killerinfographics.com/ebooks-whitepapers"><span style="font-weight: 400;">ebooks</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, it offers insight into a specific corner of visual communication ? in this case, the benefits of visual communication shown through a data-driven approach. </span></p>

		</div>
	</div>
<div class="divider-wrap"><div style="height: 40px;" class="divider"></div></div><div class="img-with-aniamtion-wrap " data-max-width="100%" data-border-radius="none"><div class="inner"><img data-shadow="none" data-shadow-direction="middle" class="img-with-animation " data-delay="0" height="551" width="1200" data-animation="fade-in" src="http://killerinfographics.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-04.jpg" srcset="http://2fhd5y2itip42q28gh4cz5ln.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-04.jpg 1200w, http://2fhd5y2itip42q28gh4cz5ln.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-04-300x138.jpg 300w, http://2fhd5y2itip42q28gh4cz5ln.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-04-768x353.jpg 768w, http://2fhd5y2itip42q28gh4cz5ln.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-04-1024x470.jpg 1024w" sizes="100vw" alt="content marketing" /></div></div><div class="divider-wrap"><div style="height: 40px;" class="divider"></div></div>
	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We built this microsite to help explain the value of different types of visual communication (infographics, motion graphics, interactive content) to the world, providing examples and showing why quality matters for success. As a highly targeted resource, the microsite is an easy way to show your boss, colleagues, or employees the true value of well-executed visual communication.</span></p>

		</div>
	</div>
<div class="divider-wrap"><div style="height: 40px;" class="divider"></div></div><div class="img-with-aniamtion-wrap " data-max-width="100%" data-border-radius="none"><div class="inner"><img data-shadow="none" data-shadow-direction="middle" class="img-with-animation " data-delay="0" height="590" width="1200" data-animation="fade-in" src="http://killerinfographics.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-05.jpg" srcset="http://2fhd5y2itip42q28gh4cz5ln.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-05.jpg 1200w, http://2fhd5y2itip42q28gh4cz5ln.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-05-300x148.jpg 300w, http://2fhd5y2itip42q28gh4cz5ln.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-05-768x378.jpg 768w, http://2fhd5y2itip42q28gh4cz5ln.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Microsite-Blog-The-Future-of-Content-Marketing-05-1024x503.jpg 1024w" sizes="100vw" alt="content marketing stats" /></div></div><div class="divider-wrap"><div style="height: 40px;" class="divider"></div></div>
